                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/157749474/a3d29e698acee488ea48e7cd36af0835_1331396661086002329.png",
                "title": "游丝征灵"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着草元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">绽放</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下次火元素或雷元素伤害+2的[<span style=\"color: white\">草原核</span>]</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">燃烧</span>：本伤害+1，生成回合结束时造成1点火元素伤害的[<span style=\"color: white\">燃烧烈焰</span>]（可用次数1，最多叠加到2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">原激化</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下2次草元素或雷元素伤害+1的[<span style=\"color: white\">激化领域</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/157749474/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_6505256302815706037.png",
                "id": "talent66577",
                "key": "草元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "草元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">游丝征灵</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素伤害</span>，治疗我方出战角色1点。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">脉摄宣明</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">行动阶段开始时：</span>生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">无郤气护盾</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">无郤气护盾</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">护盾</span></p><p>提供<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">1点护盾</span>，保护我方出战角色。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">此效果被移除，或被重复生成时：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素伤害</span>，治疗我方出战角色1点。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">护盾</span></strong></p><p>此护盾所保护的角色受到伤害时，将会消耗护盾来抵消伤害。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_4129349443386172461.png",
